name: Paint To Pixel
summary: Paint To Pixel is a Virtual Reality exhibition that charts the history of UK graffiti. It features interviews with prominent UK artists and personal photo archives that cover 6 decades of graffiti writing. Trains from Graff Central station, covered in original whole-car art, travel to 5 different galleries that cover themes from the roots of graffiti in 1970s New York, to the explosion of Street Art in popular culture and urban festivals. Hear interviews about the illegal art of train graffiti and learn...
